<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<Subtitle>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>1</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>11642</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>19185</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>孙悟空将手放在了那根金箍棒上。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>2</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>19186</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>22776</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他感觉到金箍棒在动。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>3</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>22777</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>24961</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“嗯。”他想，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>4</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>24962</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>27106</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“这根金箍棒有魔力。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>5</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>27107</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>31314</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我敢说，我让它做什么，它就会做什么。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>6</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>31315</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>34463</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“变小！”悟空命令道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>7</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>34464</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>37388</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>金箍棒真的变小了！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>8</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>37389</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>41747</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>它现在只比悟空高一点点。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>9</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>41748</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>46854</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他拿起了金箍棒挥舞起来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>10</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>46855</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>52256</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“这才是我完美的兵器。”他说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>11</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>52257</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>59159</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我简直不敢相信，他居然拿起了金箍棒！”龙后说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>12</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>59160</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>65557</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟空让金箍棒变得更小了，变得像针一样大。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>13</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>65558</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>70852</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他把金箍棒放进了耳朵里。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>14</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>70853</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>74778</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我找到了我想要的。”悟空说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>15</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>74779</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>81100</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“再见。”他转身离开了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>16</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>81101</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>86125</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“他实在是太无礼了！”龙后说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>17</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>86126</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>89445</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>龙王握紧了拳头。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>18</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>89446</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>92336</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我要到玉帝那儿告他！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>19</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>92337</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>98519</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟空回到花果山，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>20</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>98520</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>102972</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他的孩儿们都为悟空的新兵器惊叹。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>21</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>102973</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>108785</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“不会再有人来欺负我们了！”悟空说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>22</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>108786</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>111692</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>猴子们大声欢呼。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>23</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>111693</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>118372</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他们办了一场宴会直到深夜。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>24</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>118373</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>124148</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟空开心地躺到了床上。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>25</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>124149</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>130451</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>但他刚入睡的时候，就有两个小鬼抓住了他。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>26</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>130452</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>138325</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你们干什么？”悟空问，“放开我！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>27</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>138326</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>145574</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他用力地挣扎着，但却被那两个小鬼拖了出去。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>28</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>145575</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>151499</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他们朝着一座可怕的阴森森的城走去，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>29</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>151500</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>155886</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>大门上写着“幽冥界”。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>30</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>155887</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>159983</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“幽冥界？”悟空大叫。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>31</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>159984</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>165445</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“这是死人来的地方。我是长生不老的。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>32</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>165446</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>169594</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他用力挣脱了双臂。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>33</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>169595</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>172714</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“长！”他大声叫道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>34</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>172715</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>176402</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他的金箍棒迅速变大。砰!</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>35</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>176403</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>179514</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他用力打倒了第一个小鬼。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>36</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>179515</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>183102</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>咚! 他又打倒了第二个小鬼。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>37</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>183103</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>187651</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟空进入了幽冥界。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>38</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>187652</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>193733</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他向着阎王殿走去。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>39</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>193734</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>199333</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他边走边挥舞着金箍棒。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>40</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>199334</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>202644</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>妖魔鬼怪到处逃。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>41</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>202645</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>207584</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>一个高大的鬼魂走出了阎王殿。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>42</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>207585</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>211856</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“这里出了什么事情？”鬼魂问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>43</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>211857</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>214648</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你是谁？”悟空问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>44</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>214649</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>218862</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我是阎王。”鬼魂说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>45</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>218863</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>222381</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你为什么惹出这些麻烦？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>46</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>222382</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>226324</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我想知道，为什么带我来这里？”悟空说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>47</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>226325</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>228403</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“现在就告诉我！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>48</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>228404</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>230991</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>阎王举起了双手。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>49</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>230992</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>233895</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“如果你是被带来这里的，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>50</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>233896</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>238689</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>那就是说你在人间的期限到了。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>51</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>238690</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>241582</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“不可能！”悟空大叫。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>52</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>241583</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>243917</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我是长生不老的！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>53</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>243918</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>247470</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>阎王看上去有点紧张。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>54</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>247471</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>250997</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我查查生死簿。”他说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>55</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>250998</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>259731</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“生死簿上有人间每个生灵的名字、年纪和死亡的时间。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>56</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>259732</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>265048</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>在阎王殿里，阎王翻开了生死簿。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>57</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>265049</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>268495</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你的名字是？”他问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>58</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>268496</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>270532</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟空告诉了他。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>59</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>270533</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>274093</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>阎王快速地翻着生死簿。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>60</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>274094</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>277508</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“找到了。”阎王说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>61</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>277509</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>285727</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“这上面说‘孙悟空。三百年前出生。今日死亡。’”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>62</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>285728</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>288197</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟空摇头。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>63</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>288198</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>291359</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“不可能。我是长生不老的。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>64</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>291360</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>295518</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“生死簿是不会错的。”阎王说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>65</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>295519</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>300115</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你现在必须永远留在这里了。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>66</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>300116</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>306605</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟空抓起了自己的金箍棒，瞪着阎王。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>67</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>306606</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>309177</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“把生死薄给我！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>68</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>309178</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>311315</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>阎王犹豫了一下。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>69</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>311316</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>313157</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我不能给......”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>70</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>313158</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>315987</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“快给我！”悟空说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>71</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>315988</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>321845</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>阎王浑身发抖，把生死簿给了悟空。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>72</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>321846</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>326055</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟空拔了两根毫毛，吹了口气。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>73</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>326056</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>329445</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>它们变成了毛笔和墨水。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>74</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>329446</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>333711</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟空在他的名字上画了条线。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>75</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>333712</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>337796</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你不能这样！”阎王说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>76</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>337797</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>341513</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“不，我可以。”悟空说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>77</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>341514</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>347788</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>接下来，悟空找到了所有其他猴子的名字，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>78</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>347789</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>353842</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>把他们的名字也都划去了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>79</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>353843</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>359646</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“现在我真的要长生不老了。”孙悟空说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>80</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>359647</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>364455</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我所有的孩儿们也会长生不老的！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
</Subtitle>